教學方法 Teaching Strategies
      1.  To understand different resonant tanks for the need
2.  To comprehend different quasi resonant converters
3.  To gain proficiency working in zero-voltage-transition, zero-current-transition, and zero-current- switching-zero-voltage-switching circuits
4.  To obtain technologies of DC-link soft-switching    

